text: Viktoriya Kazakevich (born 12 May 1998) is a Belarusian footballer who plays as a defender for Premier League club Dinamo-BGU and the Belarus women's national team. ==Career== Kazakevich has been capped for the Belarus national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Belarusian women's footballers Category:Sportspeople from Minsk Category:Belarus women's international footballers
